metadata.name: CHAPTER I: The Doomsday
metadata.description:
This art is having a short story with big meaning.

Upper layer: In general this art shows the day this earth faces aridity its going to be the end of peaceful life of a human being. Somehow its gonna be the end of life. That's what the real Doomsday.

Hidden layer: Tree always resembles human being. Naturally and Psychologically. Humans dependent on these trees. When trees face dryness humans gonna lose their flesh. Somehow nature can revive their selves back. Not humans.
